WEBVTT

01:37.729 --> 01:40.630
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.300 --> 01:43.590
[Episode 22]

01:44.710 --> 01:45.400
How about

01:45.420 --> 01:47.110
we treat Master Lu to a meal?

01:49.240 --> 01:51.670
I'm afraid not. That's too much trouble.

01:51.950 --> 01:52.750
But we insist.

01:52.870 --> 01:53.920
A real gentleman knows

01:53.920 --> 01:55.180
when to return a favor.

01:55.950 --> 01:57.150
Please wait a moment, Master Lu.

01:57.150 --> 01:58.479
Food will be ready soon.

01:58.640 --> 01:59.170
Let's go!

01:59.229 --> 01:59.590
Sure.

01:59.920 --> 02:00.510
Go then.

02:00.920 --> 02:01.760
Move!

02:02.070 --> 02:02.560
Quick.

02:06.000 --> 02:06.530
Let's go.

02:07.200 --> 02:07.590
Go.

02:20.360 --> 02:21.120
Is it all?

02:22.520 --> 02:23.320
Nothing more?

02:23.400 --> 02:25.120
You insisted on treating him to a meal

02:25.120 --> 02:26.440
after he declined to be paid.

02:26.440 --> 02:27.560
How can we afford food

02:27.560 --> 02:28.690
and wine for him now?

02:29.870 --> 02:30.870
I acted on impulse.

02:30.870 --> 02:32.000
This is all my fault.

02:32.079 --> 02:33.280
What should we do now?

02:34.460 --> 02:35.240
I'll go make money

02:35.240 --> 02:36.710
by writing letters for people.

02:36.710 --> 02:37.400
I can do that too.

02:37.400 --> 02:38.020
I can even write poems.

02:38.020 --> 02:38.560
Me too.

02:38.590 --> 02:39.520
-I can also do that.
-So can I.

02:39.520 --> 02:40.579
Count me in as well.

02:40.840 --> 02:42.079
But is there enough time?

02:42.079 --> 02:42.400
I...

02:42.960 --> 02:44.360
Then what do you suggest?

02:52.680 --> 02:53.210
Master Rust-Sword!

02:53.210 --> 02:54.240
Are you crazy or what,

02:54.240 --> 02:55.030
for targeting me?

02:55.030 --> 02:57.310
-Master Rust-Sword.
-Master Rust-Sword!

02:57.310 --> 02:58.280
Sorry for the rudeness.

02:58.280 --> 02:59.190
What are you doing?

02:59.190 --> 03:00.560
Are you robbing me in broad daylight?

03:00.560 --> 03:01.360
Just lend us some money!

03:01.360 --> 03:02.590
Stop it now, or I'll fight back.

03:02.590 --> 03:03.560
Consider it a loan to us!

03:03.560 --> 03:05.400
Yes, yes, just a loan.

03:06.630 --> 03:07.430
My arm...

03:07.710 --> 03:08.960
My arm is broken!

03:09.120 --> 03:10.050
Are you alright?

03:10.080 --> 03:11.340
Faking an injury, huh?

03:11.590 --> 03:12.190
Get up now.

03:12.190 --> 03:13.210
D-Don't make me slap you.

03:13.210 --> 03:14.710
Lord of Rust-Sword, this is an emergency.

03:14.710 --> 03:15.870
We'll pay you back later.

03:15.870 --> 03:17.310
Let go of my master!

03:17.520 --> 03:18.560
I'll beat you up!

03:18.710 --> 03:20.520
This is adults' business.
Stay out of it, kiddo.

03:20.520 --> 03:21.800
I'm not a kid.

03:22.240 --> 03:23.300
Just don't butt in.

03:24.150 --> 03:24.870
Let go of me!

03:25.960 --> 03:26.750
It's here! Here!

03:26.750 --> 03:27.150
Quick!

03:27.430 --> 03:27.870
Hurry!

03:28.150 --> 03:28.880
Pull harder!

03:30.630 --> 03:32.190
We will surely pay you back later.

03:32.190 --> 03:32.710
No!

03:38.280 --> 03:38.960
My money!

03:39.960 --> 03:41.690
We'll definitely pay you back!

03:42.520 --> 03:43.430
My money...

03:44.360 --> 03:45.560
You bunch of robbers,

03:45.750 --> 03:46.950
I'm going to kill you!

03:47.070 --> 03:48.350
You'll all be dead meat!

03:48.350 --> 03:50.030
My money...

03:50.710 --> 03:51.870
What's going on outside?

03:51.870 --> 03:52.400
Nothing.

03:52.680 --> 03:54.340
They're just horsing around.

03:55.150 --> 03:56.280
My money!

03:56.520 --> 03:57.120
Come on.

03:57.710 --> 03:58.520
Have some tea.

03:59.840 --> 04:00.770
This is mint tea.

04:00.840 --> 04:02.300
It reduces internal heat.

04:02.710 --> 04:03.570
Try it, please.

04:10.680 --> 04:12.010
Did I put in enough salt?

04:12.120 --> 04:13.520
What you put in was sugar.

04:15.280 --> 04:16.390
Make the fire bigger.

04:16.390 --> 04:16.870
Got it.

04:18.190 --> 04:18.950
Stop nibbling on that carrot.

04:18.950 --> 04:20.410
G-Go fetch some firewood.

04:22.560 --> 04:23.160
Zhanying.

04:32.510 --> 04:33.190
Master Rust-Sword,

04:33.190 --> 04:34.590
come drink with us later.

04:39.870 --> 04:41.240
What a feast today.

04:41.630 --> 04:42.760
There's wine, meat,

04:43.040 --> 04:44.040
and vegetables.

04:44.560 --> 04:45.159
Master Lu,

04:45.360 --> 04:46.159
Immortal Xin,

04:46.360 --> 04:47.560
don't stand on ceremony.

04:47.560 --> 04:48.890
Be the first ones to eat.

04:49.310 --> 04:50.070
Please.

04:50.560 --> 04:52.290
Don't rabbits only eat plants?

04:52.930 --> 04:54.159
But I've become a rabbit demon now.

04:54.159 --> 04:55.360
Why can't I have meat?

04:56.560 --> 04:57.090
Alright!

04:57.240 --> 04:57.870
Let's eat!

05:04.310 --> 05:05.000
Come on.

05:05.270 --> 05:06.670
One piece for each of you.

05:07.310 --> 05:08.270
No fighting needed.

05:08.270 --> 05:09.000
Thank you.

05:09.510 --> 05:10.310
We bought this

05:10.390 --> 05:11.680
from Li's Smoked Chicken,

05:11.680 --> 05:13.560
a century-old shop in the Phoenix City.

05:13.560 --> 05:14.720
The taste is amazing.

05:14.720 --> 05:15.780
Nonsense, old man.

05:15.780 --> 05:17.110
You've never tasted it.

05:17.430 --> 05:18.270
Little demon,

05:18.600 --> 05:19.820
how do you know I've never tasted it?

05:19.820 --> 05:20.800
You can't afford it, can you?

05:20.800 --> 05:21.800
To prove yourself,

05:21.800 --> 05:24.480
why not tell us
if the drumsticks are salty or spicy?

05:24.480 --> 05:25.770
Salty, of course.

05:26.310 --> 05:26.830
Mr. Lu,

05:27.070 --> 05:27.800
try one.

05:28.220 --> 05:30.220
Let's see if this old man is correct.

05:37.420 --> 05:38.480
I'm not hungry now.

05:38.510 --> 05:38.920
An,

05:39.120 --> 05:39.980
taste it for me.

05:40.480 --> 05:41.040
Thanks.

05:48.270 --> 05:49.730
You should eat it, Master.

05:51.310 --> 05:52.440
Way to read the room.

05:54.400 --> 05:55.800
I'll take this drumstick,

05:55.800 --> 05:57.200
but not you as a disciple.

05:59.310 --> 05:59.830
An,

06:00.070 --> 06:01.070
you can have mine.

06:01.360 --> 06:02.000
Thank you.

06:03.600 --> 06:04.600
Everyone, eat up.

06:04.870 --> 06:06.270
The food's getting cold.

06:06.360 --> 06:07.560
-Hurry!
-Dig in!

06:09.360 --> 06:10.560
Thank you for your aid

06:10.600 --> 06:13.000
along the journey,
Master Lu, Immortal Xin.

06:13.000 --> 06:14.390
If it hadn't been for your help,

06:14.390 --> 06:15.360
we would probably

06:15.360 --> 06:16.160
have failed to make it

06:16.160 --> 06:17.620
to the Phoenix City alive.

06:18.190 --> 06:19.720
You even gave us two precious paintings

06:19.720 --> 06:20.600
as gifts.

06:21.000 --> 06:22.660
We doubt if we will ever be able

06:22.680 --> 06:24.560
to repay such kindness.

06:24.950 --> 06:26.000
Come on, everyone.

06:26.000 --> 06:26.920
Let's propose a toast

06:26.920 --> 06:27.650
to them both.

06:27.680 --> 06:28.190
A toast to you both.

06:28.190 --> 06:28.680
Cheers.

06:36.720 --> 06:37.780
Come on, let's eat.

06:39.000 --> 06:40.750
I also protected you along the way.

06:40.750 --> 06:42.409
Why only toast them and not me?

06:42.510 --> 06:44.240
Because we hired your service.

06:44.600 --> 06:45.800
You hired my service?

06:46.000 --> 06:47.060
Then give me my pay.

06:47.830 --> 06:49.510
The journey was a bitter experience
for me.

06:49.510 --> 06:50.830
Instead of making money,

06:50.830 --> 06:52.090
I even lost quite a sum.

06:52.690 --> 06:53.690
Not bitter at all.

06:53.720 --> 06:55.680
There's sugar in the food.
It tastes sweet.

06:55.680 --> 06:56.070
Still, I paid for...

06:56.070 --> 06:57.800
Lord of Rust-Sword, as a single man,

06:57.800 --> 06:59.270
you seem quite eager to make money.

06:59.270 --> 07:00.800
Are you trying to get a wife?

07:01.050 --> 07:02.470
I have no family, so you don't

07:02.470 --> 07:03.510
need to offer any betrothal gifts.

07:03.510 --> 07:05.710
Do you think I'd make a good wife for you?

07:05.850 --> 07:06.980
No, I don't think so.

07:07.190 --> 07:08.560
I don't plan to get married.

07:08.560 --> 07:09.090
Besides,

07:09.230 --> 07:11.510
I'm not interested in those older than me.

07:11.510 --> 07:13.770
But you're of age. Why not start a family?

07:13.830 --> 07:15.160
I just haven't met anyone I love.

07:15.160 --> 07:16.290
What a coincidence.

07:16.510 --> 07:17.370
Neither have I.

07:18.190 --> 07:18.750
An!

07:19.050 --> 07:20.780
Have a drink with Zhanying now.

07:21.360 --> 07:21.960
Zhanying,

07:22.240 --> 07:22.700
come on.

07:23.070 --> 07:23.920
Let's drink.

07:26.390 --> 07:26.950
Chen Fen,

07:27.750 --> 07:29.180
I've always been curious.

07:29.180 --> 07:29.680
Why were you given

07:29.680 --> 07:31.210
such a jinxed name as "Fen"?

07:31.560 --> 07:32.920
I'm from the Chen clan in Qinling—

07:32.920 --> 07:34.450
a long line of tomb raiders.

07:35.510 --> 07:36.870
My family have been raiding tombs

07:36.870 --> 07:37.870
for generations.

07:38.130 --> 07:39.810
About 300 years ago,

07:40.430 --> 07:42.600
South Xiang King, Li Xiang,
was dying of a severe illness.

07:42.600 --> 07:44.600
He took the advice of a ghost cultivator

07:44.600 --> 07:46.270
and decided to build a grand mausoleum

07:46.270 --> 07:47.790
for himself and set up
a Feng Shui Formation,

07:47.790 --> 07:48.870
attempting in vain to be revived
in 500 years

07:48.870 --> 07:50.040
following the Path of Ghosts.

07:50.040 --> 07:51.159
After the mausoleum was completed,

07:51.159 --> 07:51.870
in order to keep

07:51.870 --> 07:53.070
its location secret,

07:53.159 --> 07:54.159
Li Xiang had his personal guards

07:54.159 --> 07:56.070
kill all the craftsmen
who helped build it.

07:56.070 --> 07:56.930
Unexpectedly,

07:57.200 --> 07:57.870
on the guards' way back,

07:57.870 --> 07:59.680
they were trapped by a heavy downpour.

07:59.680 --> 08:00.510
Residents of the Chen Village

08:00.510 --> 08:01.640
kindly helped them.

08:01.750 --> 08:03.310
However, Li Xiang, the unscrupulous ruler,

08:03.310 --> 08:04.440
had the Chen Village

08:04.680 --> 08:05.810
nearly annihilated afterwards,

08:05.810 --> 08:06.870
just in order to conceal

08:06.870 --> 08:08.730
everything about the mausoleum.

08:09.190 --> 08:10.720
My great-great-grandfather

08:10.720 --> 08:12.050
was a child at that time.

08:12.480 --> 08:13.680
He luckily survived.

08:14.160 --> 08:15.830
Later, he focused on
the study of tomb-raiding arts,

08:15.830 --> 08:18.600
with the determination
to avenge the Chen Village.

08:18.600 --> 08:20.190
Then why did you come to the Phoenix City

08:20.190 --> 08:21.670
instead of searching for the mausoleum?

08:21.670 --> 08:22.870
I did find that place.

08:23.940 --> 08:25.240
But the traps inside work with rather

08:25.240 --> 08:26.310
complex mechanisms.

08:26.310 --> 08:27.510
I couldn't gain access.

08:27.510 --> 08:27.950
So,

08:28.120 --> 08:30.360
I came here
for the Unparalleled Secret Magic

08:30.360 --> 08:32.020
that might give me a solution.

08:32.840 --> 08:34.370
It's very tenacious of you.

08:35.080 --> 08:37.030
But what if you can't find
a solution this time?

08:37.030 --> 08:38.360
If that happens, my sons

08:38.510 --> 08:39.630
will carry on the mission.

08:39.630 --> 08:41.549
And if my sons fail,
my grandsons will continue.

08:41.549 --> 08:42.409
No matter what,

08:43.360 --> 08:44.200
my resolution to dig up

08:44.200 --> 08:45.950
that vile old man's tomb and hold him back

08:45.950 --> 08:47.810
from immortality will not waver!

08:57.440 --> 08:58.910
Why are you all giving me this look?

08:58.910 --> 09:00.910
You've heard this story before,
haven't you?

09:00.910 --> 09:02.120
I am shocked every time

09:02.120 --> 09:04.180
I hear about this king's atrocities.

09:04.360 --> 09:05.490
At this very moment,

09:05.670 --> 09:07.070
I'd like to recite a poem.

09:08.600 --> 09:10.000
Enjoy the meal, scholar.

09:11.600 --> 09:12.460
Great scholar,

09:12.790 --> 09:13.960
back in Wei County,

09:14.200 --> 09:14.840
didn't you say

09:14.840 --> 09:16.500
you'd take the imperial exam?

09:17.240 --> 09:18.440
Don't get me started.

09:18.460 --> 09:19.790
I did reach the capital.

09:19.960 --> 09:21.360
But I found that among the exam takers,

09:21.360 --> 09:22.840
half were from families
connected to immortal sects,

09:22.840 --> 09:23.440
and four out of ten

09:23.440 --> 09:25.440
were rich kids with strings to pull.

09:25.670 --> 09:27.270
Young lads from poor families like me

09:27.270 --> 09:28.530
amounted to only a few.

09:29.030 --> 09:29.560
That day,

09:29.750 --> 09:30.870
the person in front of me

09:30.870 --> 09:33.550
was cheating
with the immortal art of observation.

09:33.550 --> 09:34.410
I reported him,

09:34.510 --> 09:35.640
but the invigilator

09:35.840 --> 09:37.100
kicked me out instead.

09:37.600 --> 09:38.510
In a fit of anger,

09:38.510 --> 09:39.600
I left the capital.

09:40.080 --> 09:42.480
None of those from immortal sects
are good.

09:45.600 --> 09:46.400
Immortal Xin,

09:46.720 --> 09:48.130
his comment is not directed at you.

09:48.130 --> 09:49.260
Have I said it wrong?

09:50.090 --> 09:51.000
Those from immortal sects

09:51.000 --> 09:52.960
once set up a formation in Dahuang Valley
to draw

09:52.960 --> 09:54.200
spiritual energy from the earth veins

09:54.200 --> 09:55.200
for their cultivation,

09:55.200 --> 09:56.910
which only ended up
exploding the earth veins

09:56.910 --> 09:59.170
and causing half the valley to collapse.

09:59.390 --> 10:01.320
As a county constable at that time,

10:01.390 --> 10:03.120
I was transferred there
to handle the aftermath,

10:03.120 --> 10:04.380
along with over ten fellows

10:04.380 --> 10:07.380
who had been through
life-and-death moments with me.

10:07.510 --> 10:09.510
The spiritual energy there
was just bizzarre.

10:09.510 --> 10:10.320
Like poisonous fog,

10:10.320 --> 10:11.980
it found a way into our bodies.

10:12.200 --> 10:12.750
Shortly after,

10:12.750 --> 10:13.880
all my fellows died.

10:15.200 --> 10:15.960
I was the only one

10:15.960 --> 10:17.030
who survived.

10:17.750 --> 10:18.750
Look at me now—

10:18.750 --> 10:20.350
all messed up and miserable!

10:20.710 --> 10:22.570
I'm entitled to hatred, aren't I?

10:25.160 --> 10:26.270
Although I came to North Xiang

10:26.270 --> 10:28.070
with Wushuang Society members,

10:28.120 --> 10:29.170
my thoughts are different

10:29.170 --> 10:29.900
from theirs.

10:30.320 --> 10:31.630
They have too big an ambition.

10:31.630 --> 10:33.030
I don't quite understand.

10:33.030 --> 10:34.240
But I was told

10:34.670 --> 10:36.030
that as long as I came here,

10:36.030 --> 10:37.630
I would be given a sword,

10:38.670 --> 10:39.360
which could

10:39.750 --> 10:41.950
help me pierce the hearts of immortals.

10:44.200 --> 10:46.600
Which immortal sect set up that formation?

10:46.960 --> 10:48.120
Who assigned you to handle

10:48.120 --> 10:48.980
the aftermath?

10:49.080 --> 10:51.240
It was the Holy Fire Sect
that set up the formation.

10:51.240 --> 10:52.440
The one who assigned me to that task

10:52.440 --> 10:55.230
was Song Qingsong,
the magistrate of Xuzhou County.

10:55.230 --> 10:57.320
The Holy Fire Sect
is one of the Twelve Immortal Sects.

10:57.320 --> 10:58.940
It's managed by Master Yuntuzi,

10:58.940 --> 11:00.540
a superior cultivator at the Void Stage.

11:00.540 --> 11:02.140
He's a hundred years old now.

11:02.390 --> 11:03.720
In the Battle of Pinghu,

11:03.850 --> 11:04.980
he fought off dozens

11:05.150 --> 11:06.410
of War Demons on his own

11:06.600 --> 11:08.730
and saved the people of an entire city.

11:08.840 --> 11:10.570
He had 31 direct disciples,

11:10.600 --> 11:12.600
all of whom died protecting Xuzhou,

11:13.120 --> 11:14.150
except two—

11:15.000 --> 11:16.200
they lost arms or legs

11:17.020 --> 11:18.420
and were incapacitated.

11:19.750 --> 11:21.210
Almost all the core disciples

11:21.210 --> 11:22.360
of the Holy Fire Sect

11:22.510 --> 11:24.150
died in that battle.

11:25.370 --> 11:26.720
Yuntuzi was the only one left

11:26.720 --> 11:28.510
with the ability to support the sect.

11:28.510 --> 11:29.870
He was already old at that time.

11:29.870 --> 11:31.470
Before his final hour arrived,

11:31.470 --> 11:32.790
he had to absorb spiritual energy

11:32.790 --> 11:34.150
and sacrifice his own body

11:34.150 --> 11:35.720
to set up a protective formation

11:35.720 --> 11:37.980
so as to secure the lives of Xuzhou people

11:38.360 --> 11:40.080
and to maintain the prestige
of the Holy Fire Sect

11:40.080 --> 11:41.120
for it to last for generations.

11:41.120 --> 11:42.270
How was it wrong?

11:43.440 --> 11:44.360
So what if the story you told

11:44.360 --> 11:45.320
is true?

11:45.720 --> 11:47.260
I was indeed injured, wasn't I?

11:47.260 --> 11:48.230
My friends lost their lives,

11:48.230 --> 11:48.960
didn't they?

11:49.720 --> 11:51.510
I'm not denying your suffering.

11:51.510 --> 11:52.910
I just have one question.

11:53.360 --> 11:54.790
Are immortal sects

11:55.510 --> 11:57.570
really completely evil in your eyes?

11:58.720 --> 12:00.000
You keep saying

12:00.200 --> 12:02.060
how immortal sects try to kill you

12:02.360 --> 12:03.420
and persecute you.

12:03.910 --> 12:05.240
But have you forgotten?

12:05.390 --> 12:07.080
It was these immortal sects
that courageously

12:07.080 --> 12:08.340
fought the War Demons.

12:08.380 --> 12:09.770
It was also these immortal sects

12:09.770 --> 12:11.000
that protected the people.

12:11.000 --> 12:12.030
Mortals outnumber immortals

12:12.030 --> 12:14.000
by a hundredfold, even a thousandfold.

12:14.000 --> 12:15.120
But in the Battle of Pinghu,

12:15.120 --> 12:16.320
the number of casualties in immortal sects

12:16.320 --> 12:17.870
was almost the same as that of mortals.

12:17.870 --> 12:19.930
Immortal sects bore the brunt at war.

12:20.200 --> 12:21.720
Now that peace has been restored,

12:21.720 --> 12:22.870
you're accusing immortal sects

12:22.870 --> 12:24.510
of oppressing and persecuting you.

12:24.510 --> 12:25.790
Shouldn't the contribution

12:25.790 --> 12:27.360
of immortal sects be remembered?

12:27.360 --> 12:28.160
Immortal Xin,

12:28.270 --> 12:29.400
please don't be mad.

12:29.510 --> 12:30.580
He was just drunk and rambling.

12:30.580 --> 12:31.780
That day, you asked me

12:32.120 --> 12:34.080
if I could guarantee
that all disciples of immortal sects

12:34.080 --> 12:35.540
thought the same way I did.

12:35.840 --> 12:36.900
Right now, I'd like

12:37.360 --> 12:38.760
to ask you a question too.

12:39.270 --> 12:40.440
Can you guarantee

12:40.440 --> 12:42.370
that every human has a good nature?

12:42.510 --> 12:43.630
Oppressing the people,

12:43.630 --> 12:44.600
slaughtering mortals,

12:44.600 --> 12:45.510
and committing murder—

12:45.510 --> 12:46.580
humans and authorities are engaged

12:46.580 --> 12:48.640
in these crimes as well, aren't they?

12:53.510 --> 12:54.970
I really don't understand

12:55.320 --> 12:57.320
why the immortal sects
that have shed blood and sacrificed

12:57.320 --> 12:58.120
are described

12:58.440 --> 13:00.100
as completely evil by you lot!

13:13.960 --> 13:15.410
Those from immortal sects
haven't gone far.

13:15.410 --> 13:16.220
You could be easily spotted

13:16.220 --> 13:17.620
by rushing out like this.

13:19.390 --> 13:21.390
Sheng, where on earth are you going?

13:49.630 --> 13:51.290
Was I being too harsh just now?

13:51.910 --> 13:53.040
Did I scare them all?

13:54.390 --> 13:55.550
Arguments are inevitable

13:55.550 --> 13:57.790
among people holding different stances.

13:57.790 --> 13:58.600
In fact, I know

13:59.440 --> 14:00.510
why you went livid.

14:00.840 --> 14:03.160
For one thing, you were trying to defend
immortal sects.

14:03.160 --> 14:03.890
For another,

14:04.390 --> 14:06.520
part of you felt what those people said

14:06.600 --> 14:07.720
was correct.

14:14.000 --> 14:15.000
I once saw a tower ship

14:15.000 --> 14:15.910
in the desert.

14:16.360 --> 14:17.490
It was a huge vessel.

14:17.720 --> 14:19.000
There was no water around.

14:19.000 --> 14:20.150
It must've flown there.

14:20.150 --> 14:20.910
I couldn't think of

14:20.910 --> 14:23.170
any other way for it to reach North Xiang.

14:23.320 --> 14:24.270
So, I'm sure what they said

14:24.270 --> 14:25.200
is partly right,

14:25.360 --> 14:27.020
and definitely partly wrong.

14:28.440 --> 14:29.320
But actually,

14:29.750 --> 14:30.630
the problem is not about

14:30.630 --> 14:31.910
whether immortal sects are good or bad.

14:31.910 --> 14:34.750
Nor is it about
whether the Human Race is good or bad.

14:34.750 --> 14:36.790
Craftsmanship has brought hope to humans,

14:36.790 --> 14:37.850
and an opportunity

14:38.270 --> 14:39.630
for them to possess power

14:39.630 --> 14:41.510
so as not to rely on others anymore.

14:41.510 --> 14:42.550
However, immortal sects

14:42.550 --> 14:43.120
have always

14:43.120 --> 14:44.720
provided protection for the Human Race.

14:44.720 --> 14:46.750
They naturally need the latter's support.

14:46.750 --> 14:47.910
Therefore, immortal sects

14:47.910 --> 14:50.080
will not allow humans
to slip from their control

14:50.080 --> 14:51.680
and step on a different path.

14:52.390 --> 14:53.590
Consider it this way:

14:53.720 --> 14:55.150
immortal sects and humans

14:55.150 --> 14:56.030
are in a tug of war

14:56.030 --> 14:57.760
over the control of this world.

14:58.270 --> 14:59.270
Does this thought

14:59.550 --> 15:00.750
make you feel better?

15:01.270 --> 15:01.840
No.

15:02.360 --> 15:04.300
I believe there's a right and wrong
to everything.

15:04.300 --> 15:06.560
Right, wrong, good, and evil must exist.

15:07.030 --> 15:07.910
People are just

15:08.490 --> 15:10.080
whitewashing or glossing over them

15:10.080 --> 15:11.280
with certain things.

15:12.550 --> 15:13.600
However, now,

15:14.080 --> 15:15.440
I still can't see anything through

15:15.440 --> 15:16.770
or figure anything out.

15:17.030 --> 15:19.720
I've always been confused
since I joined an immortal sect.

15:19.720 --> 15:20.390
Look,

15:20.750 --> 15:23.270
if we're banned from interfering
with mundane matters,

15:23.270 --> 15:23.870
then what is

15:23.870 --> 15:25.670
the point of cultivation at all?

15:26.120 --> 15:27.580
Back in Chongling Valley,

15:27.670 --> 15:28.870
I was already baffled

15:29.100 --> 15:30.080
about how things went so bad

15:30.080 --> 15:32.080
between immortal sects and humans.

15:32.720 --> 15:33.840
What's going on now

15:35.080 --> 15:36.280
puzzles me even more.

15:38.790 --> 15:39.850
Just like you said,

15:40.320 --> 15:42.180
maybe we should wait and observe.

15:43.270 --> 15:44.470
Keep moving forward,

15:44.640 --> 15:46.440
and time will give you an answer.

16:04.600 --> 16:05.530
Anything wrong?

16:20.240 --> 16:21.700
Such weak breath support.

16:21.720 --> 16:24.000
Is he playing a funeral march?

16:28.150 --> 16:29.440
He is, after all,

16:29.440 --> 16:30.970
Father's most favored son.

16:31.240 --> 16:32.000
Old Crip,

16:32.600 --> 16:34.360
show him some respect.

16:35.570 --> 16:36.570
Most favored son?

16:37.720 --> 16:39.790
He knows nothing but cliché tunes.

16:40.270 --> 16:42.000
With that little talent of his,

16:42.000 --> 16:43.430
he shows off all the time
in front of Father.

16:43.430 --> 16:43.860
You...

16:43.910 --> 16:44.910
You have no shame!

16:45.900 --> 16:46.780
Show off how?

16:47.340 --> 16:48.310
Elaborate on it.

16:49.440 --> 16:50.320
Oh, I get it.

16:50.670 --> 16:52.670
He stays by the Soul Lamp all day long

16:53.240 --> 16:55.210
and plays the flute non-stop.

16:56.390 --> 16:57.990
Even the deaf could hear him.

16:58.110 --> 16:59.640
Bah! You're spewing filth!

16:59.870 --> 17:01.730
You'd better stop slandering my brother.

17:01.730 --> 17:02.850
Little Cicada,

17:03.280 --> 17:04.730
I'm a brother of yours too.

17:04.730 --> 17:06.730
Why do you never defend me like that?

17:08.510 --> 17:09.310
Do you...

17:09.550 --> 17:10.400
actually

17:10.680 --> 17:12.240
enjoy this tune?

17:21.890 --> 17:23.750
You're here yet you won't show up.

17:23.750 --> 17:24.310
Why?

17:24.619 --> 17:26.550
Do you plan to stay hidden forever?

17:31.200 --> 17:32.720
What's the rush?

17:33.270 --> 17:35.880
I caught two naughty kids

17:35.900 --> 17:36.860
last night.

17:37.080 --> 17:38.720
It took me nearly a whole night

17:38.720 --> 17:41.020
to snap their heads off.

17:41.310 --> 17:42.070
Xingye,

17:42.590 --> 17:43.990
you asked me to come here.

17:44.010 --> 17:46.730
It had better be for something important.

17:53.160 --> 17:54.360
Is everyone here now?

17:55.000 --> 17:55.550
Brother,

17:56.110 --> 17:57.440
Wei hasn't arrived yet.

17:57.680 --> 17:59.830
He offended me on the way,

18:00.110 --> 18:01.400
so I killed him.

18:02.790 --> 18:04.030
Impressive.

18:04.880 --> 18:06.130
You had the gall to kill him.

18:06.130 --> 18:08.660
Aren't you afraid
that Father will blame you?

18:09.110 --> 18:11.110
Wei blinded one of my eyes last year!

18:11.960 --> 18:12.830
Father said

18:13.270 --> 18:14.880
that if he dared to mess with me again,

18:14.880 --> 18:16.340
I had the right to kill him!

18:16.440 --> 18:18.000
Alright, cut the crap.

18:18.550 --> 18:19.510
Why did you

18:19.820 --> 18:21.280
require my presence here?

18:21.400 --> 18:22.930
I got a message from Father,

18:23.160 --> 18:25.270
saying that Gui's killer was found.

18:25.830 --> 18:28.160
That person is in the Phoenix City now.

18:28.640 --> 18:30.200
Father wants all of us to go there,

18:30.200 --> 18:31.000
catch her,

18:31.320 --> 18:33.250
and bring her back to Qianyan Cave.

18:33.310 --> 18:35.440
Now that Father knows where she is,

18:35.720 --> 18:37.180
why must he make us go there

18:37.590 --> 18:39.510
instead of taking action himself?

18:39.510 --> 18:40.890
Isn't it too much trouble?

18:40.890 --> 18:43.090
How dare you question Father's orders!

18:44.070 --> 18:45.330
Still bickering, huh?

18:46.790 --> 18:48.440
The killer is said to be

18:48.440 --> 18:50.160
a female cultivator
from the Central Plains.

18:50.160 --> 18:51.960
What is her cultivation level?

18:52.240 --> 18:54.370
The Foundation Establishment Stage.

18:54.830 --> 18:56.000
The female cultivator
they are talking about

18:56.000 --> 18:57.400
must be my senior sister.

18:57.720 --> 18:58.680
Does it mean I am not

18:58.680 --> 19:00.480
the one who that old man is after?

19:01.000 --> 19:03.280
How is
a mere Foundation Establishment cultivator

19:03.280 --> 19:04.000
worthy of

19:04.000 --> 19:05.510
the joint efforts of all of us?

19:05.510 --> 19:07.170
It is pointed out in Father's message

19:07.170 --> 19:09.240
that despite
her mediocre cultivation strength,

19:09.240 --> 19:10.700
this woman is accompanied

19:10.720 --> 19:12.110
by a Nascent Soul master

19:12.590 --> 19:13.720
with amazing powers

19:13.920 --> 19:15.180
and smart strategies.

19:15.310 --> 19:16.510
In case of accidents,

19:16.880 --> 19:18.940
Father would like us to work as a team.

19:20.640 --> 19:22.170
A Nascent Soul cultivator?

19:22.590 --> 19:24.250
I can't take on this task then.

19:24.750 --> 19:27.160
Seeing how weak I am,

19:27.510 --> 19:28.710
they might capture me

19:28.790 --> 19:30.000
and try to hurt me.

19:30.270 --> 19:32.530
I won't be able to fight back
in that case.

19:32.790 --> 19:33.720
Little Cicada,

19:34.150 --> 19:35.280
you can't go either.

19:35.440 --> 19:35.840
You...

19:36.730 --> 19:38.200
According to Father's message,

19:38.200 --> 19:39.460
all of us must go there.

19:39.640 --> 19:41.770
Whoever kills that female cultivator

19:41.790 --> 19:42.720
will be rewarded

19:43.400 --> 19:44.550
by Father.

19:45.000 --> 19:45.640
Fine.

19:46.000 --> 19:47.130
That being the case,

19:47.510 --> 19:49.510
we'd better not waste any more time.

19:49.720 --> 19:50.520
Let's set off!

19:51.030 --> 19:51.790
Go!

20:07.640 --> 20:09.310
The female cultivator they are looking for

20:09.310 --> 20:10.570
is your senior sister.

20:10.920 --> 20:12.050
Will you go save her?

20:14.000 --> 20:15.070
There are six of them.

20:15.070 --> 20:17.000
Two are at the Golden Core Stage,
and four at the Nascent Soul Stage.

20:17.000 --> 20:19.000
They're all stronger than you and me.

20:19.000 --> 20:19.550
Sheng,

20:20.440 --> 20:21.370
you need my help.

20:22.070 --> 20:23.070
Think it through.

20:24.630 --> 20:25.960
I was born with bad luck.

20:26.030 --> 20:26.830
Misfortune falls on

20:26.830 --> 20:28.030
everyone close to me.

20:29.960 --> 20:31.820
Are you sure you'll stick with me?

20:33.510 --> 20:34.000
Yes.

20:37.590 --> 20:38.990
Then keep your mouth shut

20:39.350 --> 20:40.150
and follow me.

20:43.920 --> 20:44.720
They are back.

20:45.510 --> 20:45.920
Hurry.

20:45.940 --> 20:47.400
Look sincere. Stand straight.

20:47.400 --> 20:48.060
No problem.

20:58.550 --> 21:00.350
Immortal Xin, please be seated.

21:00.400 --> 21:01.030
Thanks.

21:05.830 --> 21:06.480
Master Lu,

21:07.200 --> 21:08.000
Immortal Xin,

21:08.110 --> 21:10.570
on behalf of my fellows
in Wushuang Society,

21:10.920 --> 21:13.790
I'd like to apologize to you
for the previous remarks.

21:13.790 --> 21:14.720
Have this drink,

21:14.920 --> 21:16.450
and we'll still be friends.

21:25.030 --> 21:26.880
Did anything happen just now?

21:32.150 --> 21:32.680
No.

21:33.160 --> 21:34.560
Nothing happened at all.

21:34.840 --> 21:35.320
Right?

21:36.590 --> 21:37.160
Right.

21:37.450 --> 21:38.350
Nothing happened.

21:38.350 --> 21:39.640
-Right!
-Nothing happened.

21:39.640 --> 21:40.680
Everyone, sit down.

21:40.680 --> 21:41.830
Let's have a drink together.

21:41.830 --> 21:42.110
Sure.

21:42.110 --> 21:42.830
Come on.

21:42.920 --> 21:43.550
Of course.

21:44.240 --> 21:44.680
Cheers!

21:44.680 --> 21:45.160
Cheers!

21:50.680 --> 21:52.480
What's the fun in just drinking?

21:52.830 --> 21:54.110
Rust-Sword, little buddy.

21:54.110 --> 21:55.460
How about I sing you a song?

21:55.460 --> 21:57.150
It's a folk song from my hometown.

21:57.150 --> 21:59.200
Men sing it when they propose marriage.

21:59.200 --> 22:01.550
Women sing it
when they meet the men they're into.

22:01.550 --> 22:02.030
-Great!
-Go ahead!

22:02.030 --> 22:03.230
No, no, please don't.

22:03.680 --> 22:05.080
Men at 18 are like blooms.

22:05.480 --> 22:06.080
Zhanying,

22:06.510 --> 22:07.770
please show some mercy

22:07.830 --> 22:09.490
and try not to destroy a bloom.

22:09.550 --> 22:10.030
You...

22:10.750 --> 22:11.880
You can sing for him!

22:12.590 --> 22:13.520
Or if you have to,

22:13.590 --> 22:14.350
sing for Lu!

22:14.840 --> 22:15.900
He's older than me.

22:16.130 --> 22:17.050
As it happens,

22:17.190 --> 22:18.190
I'm only into you!

22:21.350 --> 22:23.030
-Lord of Rust-Sword, don't run away!
-Don't go!

22:23.030 --> 22:23.550
Freeze!

22:23.920 --> 22:24.720
Stop running!

22:25.400 --> 22:25.960
An, An!

22:25.960 --> 22:26.800
Still running, huh?

22:26.800 --> 22:27.550
Zhanying,

22:27.720 --> 22:28.510
l-let me

22:28.790 --> 22:30.050
propose a toast to you.

22:30.400 --> 22:30.960
Alright.

22:31.830 --> 22:33.720
Everyone, if you don't mind,

22:34.550 --> 22:36.070
let me sing for you.

22:36.720 --> 22:37.120
Great!

22:37.510 --> 22:38.040
Go ahead.

22:40.720 --> 22:47.640
♪ Peerless Goddess Wushuang,
unmatched in all the world ♪

22:48.400 --> 22:54.790
♪ Exquisite tower ships
soar across the heavens ♪

22:55.580 --> 22:58.580
♪ Within her wondrous halls,
thousands find their place ♪

22:58.790 --> 23:04.270
♪ Cannons and blades alike—
unrivaled in battle ♪

23:04.270 --> 23:06.510
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

23:07.550 --> 23:08.070
Come on.

23:08.550 --> 23:09.200
Drink up.

23:27.640 --> 23:28.300
Hold still.

23:33.790 --> 23:34.270
Go!

23:40.310 --> 23:40.880
Move.

24:05.680 --> 24:06.540
Keep up with me.

24:14.270 --> 24:15.330
What is this place?

24:16.310 --> 24:17.200
The Purgatory,

24:17.960 --> 24:19.750
where I grew up.

25:03.030 --> 25:03.590
Wait!

25:11.390 --> 25:12.690
I owe you a favor now.

25:48.550 --> 25:49.280
This is it.

26:00.030 --> 26:01.230
It's cooler outside.

26:02.310 --> 26:03.510
You drank so much wine

26:03.640 --> 26:04.640
in that stuff room.

26:04.640 --> 26:06.570
You'd certainly feel hot in there.

26:06.640 --> 26:07.880
That said, this place is still much cooler

26:07.880 --> 26:08.810
than Xutuo City.

26:10.350 --> 26:12.070
This is the Chill Street.

26:12.510 --> 26:14.040
Of course it's cooler here.

26:14.640 --> 26:16.500
What's the story behind the name?

26:17.200 --> 26:18.880
This used to be a wasteland.

26:19.680 --> 26:20.960
Passing merchants

26:21.030 --> 26:22.760
liked to rest and cool off here.

26:23.200 --> 26:24.030
So it developed into

26:24.030 --> 26:24.960
what it is today.

26:25.960 --> 26:28.110
Ahead is Xilian Range,

26:28.500 --> 26:29.880
consisting of high hills

26:29.880 --> 26:31.160
that stretch for thousands of miles

26:31.160 --> 26:32.620
and block most of the heat.

26:33.210 --> 26:34.050
Due to that,

26:34.200 --> 26:35.440
this area is much cooler

26:35.440 --> 26:36.640
than any other place.

26:37.000 --> 26:37.830
Over time,

26:38.270 --> 26:39.730
people started calling it

26:39.790 --> 26:40.960
the Chill Street.

26:42.070 --> 26:43.400
There are perks to living a long life.

26:43.400 --> 26:44.860
You get to see everything.

26:45.750 --> 26:47.550
Is that a compliment?

26:48.350 --> 26:49.280
It certainly is.

26:50.430 --> 26:51.390
Have you been

26:51.550 --> 26:52.280
here before?

26:54.200 --> 26:54.960
Yes, once.

26:55.870 --> 26:56.480
But it was

26:56.510 --> 26:57.510
a long time ago.

26:59.970 --> 27:01.200
We have nothing to do tonight anyway.

27:01.200 --> 27:02.860
Why don't you tell me about it?

27:05.000 --> 27:05.510
Sure.

27:06.640 --> 27:08.040
Let me take you to a place.

27:21.790 --> 27:22.400
This is it.

27:25.450 --> 27:27.420
[Market Quarter Scenes]

27:26.160 --> 27:27.560
Did you paint all of this?

27:29.030 --> 27:31.090
When I was in the Phoenix City before,

27:31.110 --> 27:33.040
I used to drink in this very tavern.

27:33.550 --> 27:34.310
At that time,

27:34.790 --> 27:35.960
under the influence of wine,

27:35.960 --> 27:38.160
I drew this, the Market Quarter Scenes.

27:38.550 --> 27:39.480
Unfortunately,

27:39.590 --> 27:41.240
my flesh hadn't been replaced by then,

27:41.240 --> 27:42.900
so I couldn't identify colors

27:42.940 --> 27:43.850
or depict

27:43.880 --> 27:45.740
the entirety of the mortal world.

27:48.480 --> 27:50.080
When I was learning to paint,

27:50.110 --> 27:51.400
my tutors at the painting hall

27:51.400 --> 27:53.260
always compared life to a scroll.

27:53.680 --> 27:55.140
They often described life

27:55.440 --> 27:56.400
to be

27:57.100 --> 27:57.890
"colorful"

27:58.260 --> 27:59.660
or "vibrantly colored."

27:59.820 --> 28:01.450
Since I couldn't tell colors apart,

28:01.450 --> 28:03.080
I was never able to draw

28:03.190 --> 28:04.320
a complete drawing.

28:04.960 --> 28:06.780
But your ink wash painting is already

28:06.780 --> 28:08.510
masterful and beyond compare.

28:10.050 --> 28:11.110
This is not enough.

28:11.290 --> 28:12.490
It's far from enough.

28:12.770 --> 28:14.760
Not only do I yearn to see the world
as it is,

28:14.760 --> 28:17.360
I also want to enjoy
everything it has to offer.

28:17.490 --> 28:19.000
I'd hate for my life to be incomplete

28:19.000 --> 28:20.510
like this painting is.

28:21.830 --> 28:23.310
I hope to fill my life with warmth

28:23.310 --> 28:23.970
and colors.

28:24.830 --> 28:25.350
I wish

28:25.900 --> 28:27.500
I could live a fulfilled life

28:27.540 --> 28:28.610
like a mortal.

28:29.670 --> 28:32.070
I hate to get hysterical
and thirsty for blood again.

28:32.070 --> 28:33.160
I want to learn etiquette

28:33.160 --> 28:34.660
and to tell right from wrong.

28:34.660 --> 28:35.300
I long to see

28:35.300 --> 28:37.100
the myriad colors in this world.

28:37.220 --> 28:38.070
I also crave

28:38.460 --> 28:39.600
to experience every feeling

28:39.600 --> 28:40.790
that ties me to this world,

28:40.790 --> 28:41.590
be it pain,

28:42.000 --> 28:42.550
agony,

28:43.160 --> 28:43.890
resentment,

28:44.140 --> 28:44.740
or sorrow.

28:45.820 --> 28:47.470
I want to have a sense of taste as well.

28:47.470 --> 28:49.070
I wish I could taste every delicacy

28:49.070 --> 28:49.880
in this world.

28:51.400 --> 28:52.800
If that day really comes,

28:53.060 --> 28:53.880
I'd like to hire

28:53.880 --> 28:55.640
the most expensive restaurant
in the capital

28:55.640 --> 28:57.170
to serve me the best cuisine

28:57.310 --> 28:58.590
and the strongest wine,

28:58.590 --> 28:59.520
so I can get drunk

28:59.960 --> 29:01.160
and have a good sleep.

29:05.000 --> 29:08.670
♪ Let strong wine carry me into
drunken nights till midnight ♪

29:08.690 --> 29:11.750
♪ Let my soul blaze in brilliant colors ♪

29:11.780 --> 29:14.610
♪ Let the agony of a thousand cuts ♪

29:14.630 --> 29:19.220
♪ Stand as proof that I have lived ♪

29:19.520 --> 29:23.120
♪ Let me taste a life of flesh and blood
in full ♪

29:23.140 --> 29:26.300
♪ Let me savor the many flavors
of the mortal world ♪

29:26.410 --> 29:28.240
♪ Let me face the world's
warmth and cold alike ♪

29:28.260 --> 29:33.600
♪ To live and perish with it,
daring to go mad, daring to dream ♪

29:34.060 --> 29:37.710
♪ Let strong wine carry me into
drunken nights till midnight ♪

29:37.740 --> 29:40.780
♪ Let my soul blaze in brilliant colors ♪

29:40.900 --> 29:43.700
♪ Let the agony of a thousand cuts ♪

29:43.720 --> 29:48.140
♪ Stand as proof that I have lived ♪

29:44.000 --> 29:45.130
After so many years,

29:45.510 --> 29:46.310
this painting

29:46.720 --> 29:47.920
is finally complete.

29:48.510 --> 29:52.260
♪ Let me taste a life of flesh and blood
in full ♪

29:49.720 --> 29:50.780
Your life will also

29:51.070 --> 29:52.290
become complete little by little.

29:52.290 --> 29:55.220
♪ Let me savor the many flavors
of the mortal world ♪

29:55.460 --> 29:57.500
♪ Let me face the world's
warmth and cold alike ♪

29:57.530 --> 30:02.560
♪ To live and perish with it,
daring to go mad, daring to dream ♪

30:02.590 --> 30:08.760
♪ Don't live in vain,
have a pleasant journey of life ♪

30:06.000 --> 30:06.640
That painting

30:06.640 --> 30:08.200
was made by Master Buquan!

30:08.350 --> 30:09.880
You must pay for damaging it.

30:09.880 --> 30:11.160
Guards, take them down!

30:11.160 --> 30:11.640
Run!

30:11.790 --> 30:12.450
Stop there!

30:13.070 --> 30:13.550
Stop!

30:15.230 --> 30:15.710
Freeze!

30:38.070 --> 30:38.590
Don't you have

30:38.590 --> 30:39.790
any questions for me?

30:43.030 --> 30:43.960
Many, actually.

30:44.880 --> 30:45.550
But I think

30:46.400 --> 30:47.930
you will tell me everything

30:48.000 --> 30:49.110
when you feel like doing so.

30:49.110 --> 30:49.880
If you don't,

30:50.550 --> 30:51.680
it's of no use to ask.

30:53.410 --> 30:55.030
I have to say you're brilliant.

30:55.030 --> 30:56.560
I've learned a lesson or two

30:57.030 --> 30:59.090
after spending so much time with you.

31:00.030 --> 31:01.230
That day, you asked me

31:01.790 --> 31:03.390
if I felt pain from injuries.

31:04.080 --> 31:05.740
I am not made of wood or stones.

31:06.070 --> 31:08.200
Of course I feel pain when I'm injured.

31:08.750 --> 31:10.070
But compared with the suffering

31:10.070 --> 31:11.800
I experienced in Qianyan Cave,

31:12.140 --> 31:13.870
a sword wound through the chest

31:14.070 --> 31:15.930
could barely amount to anything.

31:17.190 --> 31:17.710
Were you attacked

31:17.710 --> 31:19.110
by those people in the woods?

31:19.110 --> 31:19.680
What exactly

31:19.680 --> 31:21.140
do they have to do with you?

31:23.680 --> 31:24.480
Stop running!

31:24.960 --> 31:25.590
Freeze!

31:25.830 --> 31:26.270
Halt!

31:26.640 --> 31:27.180
There they are!

31:27.180 --> 31:29.180
-Stop running!
-Catch up with them!

31:31.510 --> 31:32.510
They've gone far.

31:36.150 --> 31:36.680
Oh right.

31:37.270 --> 31:38.200
In your opinion,

31:38.210 --> 31:40.700
to get rid of
the Punishment of the Five Deficiencies

31:40.700 --> 31:41.790
why would the War Demons choose

31:41.790 --> 31:43.880
to plant Jianmu Tree
and attempt to ascend to heaven,

31:43.880 --> 31:45.680
over the solution you proposed?

31:46.830 --> 31:48.160
Power is like poison.

31:49.070 --> 31:51.330
One can't live without it when one has it.

31:51.920 --> 31:52.650
I think maybe

31:52.920 --> 31:53.510
I just see things

31:53.510 --> 31:55.170
differently than my fellows.

31:55.400 --> 31:56.310
In their eyes,

31:56.880 --> 31:58.000
reincarnating as humans

31:58.000 --> 31:59.600
is a process of losing power.

32:00.440 --> 32:01.310
But in my eyes,

32:01.960 --> 32:02.960
it is a critical part

32:02.960 --> 32:04.220
of completing my life.

32:05.550 --> 32:06.200
Actually,

32:06.830 --> 32:08.240
I am of mixed ancestry.

32:10.240 --> 32:11.640
My mother was a War Demon.

32:11.960 --> 32:12.690
But my father

32:13.110 --> 32:13.880
was a human.

32:14.960 --> 32:16.560
How did a War Demon and a human

32:17.030 --> 32:18.030
end up a couple?

32:19.270 --> 32:20.480
They met each other

32:20.790 --> 32:22.240
when all gods disappeared,

32:22.240 --> 32:24.680
and the human world
was struck by ceaseless war.

32:24.680 --> 32:26.310
My mother fell in love with my father.

32:26.310 --> 32:26.880
For him,

32:27.240 --> 32:28.350
she ran away from home,

32:28.350 --> 32:29.550
abandoned her responsibility,

32:29.550 --> 32:30.830
retreated to the wilderness,

32:30.830 --> 32:31.960
and gave birth to me.

32:33.920 --> 32:35.120
I suppose your mother

32:35.350 --> 32:36.410
must have loved you

32:37.160 --> 32:38.360
and your father a lot.

32:39.750 --> 32:40.950
She did, originally.

32:41.110 --> 32:42.240
But unfortunately,

32:42.590 --> 32:44.650
my father was a spy for the Human Race.

32:44.830 --> 32:46.160
He approached my mother

32:46.200 --> 32:47.350
just to gather intelligence

32:47.350 --> 32:48.830
about War Demons.

32:49.830 --> 32:51.830
As my mother found out the truth,
she got furious

32:51.830 --> 32:53.830
and killed my father and his fellows.

32:53.830 --> 32:54.350
Then,

32:55.030 --> 32:56.690
she left me in blazing flames.

33:35.110 --> 33:36.030
That fire

33:36.340 --> 33:37.210
almost burned off

33:37.210 --> 33:38.120
all my skin.

33:39.110 --> 33:41.110
The silver lining was, I got new skin

33:41.480 --> 33:43.080
and finally some good sleep.

33:44.090 --> 33:44.770
After that,

33:45.110 --> 33:46.840
I started roaming the streets.

33:47.160 --> 33:48.200
I couldn't turn to my mother

33:48.200 --> 33:49.600
at the War Demons' place.

33:49.830 --> 33:51.830
Humans saw me as enemy.

33:52.350 --> 33:54.270
At that time, I was all alone.

33:54.920 --> 33:55.850
There was no room

33:56.030 --> 33:57.960
for me in this vast world.

33:58.550 --> 34:00.210
So I had to conceal my identity

34:00.680 --> 34:02.200
and look for my father.

34:04.440 --> 34:05.570
What happened then?

34:06.240 --> 34:08.710
Then, I met my master.

34:09.550 --> 34:10.510
You had a master?

34:12.110 --> 34:13.510
Her name was Duan Xianyin.

34:13.510 --> 34:15.550
She had been in seclusion
at Liubo Temple for years.

34:15.550 --> 34:17.280
Very few people knew about her.

34:17.360 --> 34:18.760
She took me in as a disciple,

34:18.760 --> 34:20.290
taught me to read and write,

34:20.320 --> 34:22.070
and instructed me on magic techniques.

34:22.070 --> 34:22.760
After that,

34:23.280 --> 34:24.840
I began wandering in the human world.

34:24.840 --> 34:25.920
Because my lifespan

34:25.920 --> 34:27.320
is longer than mortals',

34:27.590 --> 34:29.469
and my appearance doesn't age easily,

34:29.469 --> 34:30.810
I had to frequently

34:30.840 --> 34:32.920
change my name and identity.

34:33.670 --> 34:35.929
At first, I worked in the Imperial Palace

34:36.230 --> 34:37.360
where I met Su Taiyi.

34:37.880 --> 34:38.409
Later on,

34:38.710 --> 34:40.110
being deprived of power,

34:40.139 --> 34:42.540
I took Su Taiyi away with me
from the palace.

34:42.550 --> 34:43.610
Then, I met Mrs. Li.

34:44.920 --> 34:47.000
The Landlady of the Safe Haven Inn?

34:47.670 --> 34:48.070
Yes.

34:49.030 --> 34:50.630
After that, I got very bored,

34:51.070 --> 34:53.070
so I decided to be a hero
in the martial world.

34:53.070 --> 34:54.880
The many years of adventuring in it
opened my eyes

34:54.880 --> 34:57.230
to the fun
and the tight interpersonal connection

34:57.230 --> 34:58.290
in this community.

34:58.710 --> 35:00.150
That made my desire to live as a mortal

35:00.150 --> 35:01.880
become stronger and stronger.

35:02.360 --> 35:04.800
Then I joined the army

35:05.070 --> 35:06.600
and worked as a magistrate.

35:06.670 --> 35:07.280
What next?

35:08.440 --> 35:09.360
Next,

35:09.670 --> 35:10.440
I met you

35:11.280 --> 35:12.940
and died a death by 1,000 cuts.

35:13.110 --> 35:14.110
You know all about

35:14.400 --> 35:15.860
what happened after that.

35:16.590 --> 35:18.230
But I've lost those memories.

35:18.230 --> 35:19.630
I can't recall anything.

35:21.920 --> 35:23.110
When I see Chu Ying,

35:23.590 --> 35:25.050
I will definitely have him

35:25.230 --> 35:27.160
restore your memories right away.

35:39.410 --> 35:41.130
I grew up in Qianyan Cave.

35:41.790 --> 35:43.120
I was a slave and servant

35:43.600 --> 35:45.640
living a worse life than an animal's.

35:45.640 --> 35:46.700
The people here often

35:46.700 --> 35:48.070
tested drugs on me.

35:48.830 --> 35:51.090
The master of Qianyan Cave is Xia Xuanzi.

35:51.980 --> 35:53.770
With that pretty face of his,

35:54.490 --> 35:55.890
he looks like a young man.

35:56.080 --> 35:56.830
But he is

35:57.280 --> 35:58.610
the most vicious of all.

35:59.770 --> 36:00.400
You've heard about

36:00.400 --> 36:02.190
the Crazy Taoist's prophecies, right?

36:02.190 --> 36:02.800
Yes.

36:03.380 --> 36:05.320
A destructive disaster
will befall the world.

36:05.320 --> 36:07.030
Those who are born on September 9th

36:07.030 --> 36:08.610
will be saviors of the world.

36:08.610 --> 36:09.490
Actually,

36:09.760 --> 36:11.760
he left three prophecies back then.

36:11.760 --> 36:13.560
The first two are for the people.

36:14.420 --> 36:15.150
The third one

36:16.120 --> 36:17.800
is for Xia Xuanzi.

36:34.150 --> 36:35.810
Those two prophecies of yours

36:36.110 --> 36:38.640
have caused quite a stir
in the martial world.

36:39.480 --> 36:41.680
Everyone says you have a brilliant mind

36:42.400 --> 36:44.730
that enables you to see
the will of heaven.

36:45.110 --> 36:46.630
In fact, I'm curious.

36:47.630 --> 36:49.190
Did you figure out

36:49.960 --> 36:51.920
why I caught you today?

36:55.590 --> 36:56.850
You are just wondering

36:57.280 --> 36:59.210
when you will leap to a higher level

36:59.710 --> 37:00.910
and become a divinity

37:01.640 --> 37:04.210
after being stuck at the Void Stage
for many years.

37:04.210 --> 37:06.250
You will never become a divinity.

37:10.360 --> 37:12.220
Trouble follows careless words.

37:12.760 --> 37:14.820
Immortal Master, watch your tongue.

37:15.150 --> 37:18.030
Xia Xuanzi of Qianyan Cave,

37:18.710 --> 37:20.520
I know what you're capable of.

37:21.160 --> 37:23.490
That day when my spirit roamed the heaven,

37:23.540 --> 37:25.940
I got a glimpse
of three future happenings.

37:26.190 --> 37:27.520
I already told the world

37:27.600 --> 37:28.970
about the first two.

37:29.590 --> 37:32.110
The third one was left unsaid on purpose,

37:33.190 --> 37:34.850
because I was waiting for you.

37:45.710 --> 37:46.710
Waiting for me?

37:48.230 --> 37:49.800
The third prophecy

37:50.180 --> 37:51.260
concerns you.

37:50.750 --> 37:54.650
[Crazy Taoist, from Dongting Mountain]

37:52.670 --> 37:54.400
That is, one of your decendents

37:54.960 --> 37:56.510
will become a divinity.

37:58.030 --> 38:00.560
Perhaps obsessed about
becoming a divinity,

38:00.590 --> 38:01.590
Xia Xuanzi started

38:01.590 --> 38:03.190
having children like crazy.

38:03.450 --> 38:04.760
He believed

38:04.780 --> 38:06.480
that only males could be divinities.

38:06.480 --> 38:08.880
So he used his power
to make women give birth

38:09.360 --> 38:10.320
to boys only.

38:10.800 --> 38:13.450
He then discarded the mothers
and kept the babies.

38:13.450 --> 38:14.670
He would even place Gu bugs

38:14.670 --> 38:15.590
in our bodies

38:16.030 --> 38:17.490
so he could manipulate us.

38:19.150 --> 38:21.000
That Gu is called the Bonding Curse.

38:21.000 --> 38:22.460
The cursed ones will share

38:22.760 --> 38:24.290
the same fate and feelings.

38:24.800 --> 38:26.280
I fell victim to it too.

38:27.360 --> 38:28.230
He connected our lives

38:28.230 --> 38:29.440
with the Gu bugs

38:29.960 --> 38:33.160
and tortured us all day long
whenever he felt displeased.

38:33.400 --> 38:36.150
I was hurt by needles, fire,

38:36.960 --> 38:37.890
and boiling oil.

38:39.110 --> 38:40.840
He would even tear off our limbs

38:41.510 --> 38:42.910
and pull out our tendons.

38:43.510 --> 38:45.360
Yet he would keep us alive

38:46.320 --> 38:47.800
so as to make us do his bidding

38:47.800 --> 38:49.460
and to torture us repeatedly.

38:50.320 --> 38:52.120
But even under such conditions,

38:52.190 --> 38:54.520
no one in Qianyan Cave
dared to fight back.

38:55.320 --> 38:56.650
What was more hilarious

38:57.320 --> 38:58.720
was that those sons of his

38:59.480 --> 39:01.590
all grew up to be just like him.

39:03.880 --> 39:04.710
I had no idea

39:05.670 --> 39:06.400
you once lived

39:06.400 --> 39:07.660
such a miserable life.

39:09.070 --> 39:10.150
Luckily,

39:10.480 --> 39:11.610
I managed to escape.

39:12.230 --> 39:13.630
I crossed the desert alone

39:13.630 --> 39:15.280
and reached the Central Plains.

39:15.280 --> 39:16.630
Then, I met my senior sister.

39:16.630 --> 39:17.960
That was how I survived.

39:18.320 --> 39:19.590
Now, Xia Xuanzi

39:20.280 --> 39:22.000
attempts to kill her.

39:23.590 --> 39:25.070
I did fear him in the past,

39:26.250 --> 39:27.580
but I don't anymore.

39:28.360 --> 39:30.150
I will kill whoever tries

39:30.960 --> 39:32.430
to hurt my senior sister.

40:01.710 --> 40:03.190
Be careful.

40:03.550 --> 40:05.030
Won't it be a shame

40:05.030 --> 40:06.070
to destroy

40:06.510 --> 40:08.040
these two beautiful faces?

40:13.480 --> 40:15.520
You really are good-looking.

40:16.170 --> 40:18.440
If it weren't for
my father's order to kill you,

40:18.440 --> 40:20.640
I really couldn't bring myself to do so.

40:23.630 --> 40:24.360
Your father?

40:25.760 --> 40:27.670
What is your relationship with Xia Xuanzi?

40:27.670 --> 40:29.440
How dare you call my father by his name!

40:29.440 --> 40:30.900
You must have a death wish!

41:17.280 --> 41:17.920
Brother,

41:18.320 --> 41:19.590
you go catch that girl.

41:20.030 --> 41:21.230
Just let me deal with

41:22.230 --> 41:23.710
this tough nut to crack.

41:27.480 --> 41:28.150
Old Crip,

41:28.320 --> 41:29.030
are you just going to watch?
